settings.text:
Fabcurate is an online fabric store based in Surat, Gujarat, that provides the latest and finest fabrics all over the world. Often we come across problems faced by customers, designers, and shop owners for not getting the type of fabric they want. Indian women often prefer to stitch their fabrics and create their style. But it is difficult to find the right type of fabrics and the process can take days and it's a waste of time. With Fabcurate, you can be sure you’ll get the highest quality fabrics, as well as the styles you want. We offer a wide range of fabrics such as cotton, silk, and more, so you’ll never be limited to just one choice. Fashion means freedom, and it should be available for all. 

Are you having trouble sourcing fabrics to create your dream designs? Big companies can be an option, but they often don’t offer the customizability or quantities you need. Fortunately, Fabcurate can help. At Fabcurate, we are here to be your exclusive partner for sourcing fabrics and designs. We offer unique designs for your clothing, home decor, and other projects. Whatever style you’re looking for, we make it simpler for you to find the perfect fabric for your projects.  


1) No Minimum Order Quantity limit for our customers, they can select any design on their choice of fabrics, and we will print the designs.

2) Wide range of options to select from. From ordinary days to festivals and holiday outfits, everything is available.

3) Best quality fabrics, at the best price.

We bring you the best prices and quality with our reliable and speedy delivery and shopping experience. We offer every kind of fabric imaginable, from silk to cotton to suede to velvet, and more. We support our Indian artisans and try to bring out their creativity in front of people, by having various Indian craft fabrics such as Kalamkari, Ikat, Tie & Dye, etc. Our customer service team is knowledgeable and experienced and is always available to help you find the right fabric for your needs. We are committed to providing our customers with a hassle-free shopping experience. 

Save Environment-

We use eco-friendly printing methods, saving a lot of water, and thereby saving the environment. The other companies/factories use water to do the printing on fabrics and thereby harming the environment. We make sure that sustainability is maintained.

We are here 'for you'!

With us, you can have all the freedom as a designer and customer, by sharing your creative ideas with us and we can imprint those designs on the fabrics. With so many trends going on, what people sometimes need is a bit change of taste in their outfits, and we are here to provide that. Our collection is updated with all kinds of fabrics and trendy designs to keep up with the pace of the fashion world. Sarees, blouses, jackets, and other accessories are available in a wide range, to keep your style up to date all year.

settings.name: Sakshi Kumari
settings.text: I want to thank the employees of the company Fabcurate for the implementation of my order. The choice of fabric was very long and selective.

settings.name: Monica Rawat
settings.text: We made a flower order at your Semetsvetik company on March 6, ordered a bouquet of Tulips for your beloved godmother, we ourselves live in another city, but I wanted to please loved ones at a distance.
